### 基础路径
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/readers

### 查询所有（分页）
GET {{baseUrl}}?page=0&size=10&sort=id&direction=asc

### 按 ID 查询
GET {{baseUrl}}/1

### 按姓名模糊查找
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?name=张三

### 新增
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "新读者",
  "gender": "女",
  "birthday": "1992-03-10",
  "registeredDate": "2024-01-15",
  "activeFlag": true,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### 更新
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "更新后姓名",
  "gender": "女",
  "activeFlag": true,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### 删除
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1
